# My Portfolio Website

This is a simple portfolio website consisting of three files:  
- `index.html` — The main homepage showcasing an introduction and projects  
- `contact.html` — A contact page with a basic contact form  
- `style.css` — CSS styles shared across both pages

## Features

- Clean and responsive layout  
- Navigation menu linking between Home and Contact pages  
- Simple contact form with name, email, and message fields (form does not have backend functionality)  
- Basic styling for easy customization

## How to Use

1. Clone or download this repository  
2. Open `index.html` in your web browser to view the portfolio homepage  
3. Use the navigation links to visit the Contact page  

## Customize

- Update `index.html` to add your own projects and introduction  
- Modify `contact.html` to customize the contact form or integrate with a backend service  
- Edit `style.css` to change colors, fonts, or layout styles

